<h2>Wyoming Incentives & Rebates</h2>
<p>Wyoming offers several attractive incentives for solar and HVAC installations, starting with the federal solar Investment Tax Credit (ITC), which provides a 30% tax credit for solar installations through 2032, then stepping down to 26% in 2033 and 22% in 2034. This credit applies to the total system cost, including equipment, installation, and permitting fees, making it one of the most valuable solar incentives available to Wyoming residents.</p>

