<p>Rocky Mountain Power offers various energy efficiency rebates for HVAC upgrades, including up to \$1,200 for high-efficiency heat pumps, \$600 for ENERGY STAR certified air conditioners, and \$400 for high-efficiency gas furnaces. The utility also provides rebates for smart thermostats (\$75-100), duct sealing services (\$300-500), and whole-house weatherization programs. Additionally, the federal government offers tax credits for geothermal heat pump installations (30% through 2032) and various HVAC efficiency upgrades, which can be combined with other incentives to maximize savings.</p>

